feat: production-ready security hardening and UI polish

Security:
- PrivacyInfo.xcprivacy: App Store required privacy manifest
- SwiftData encryption: NSFileProtectionComplete on store files
- Widget data encryption: AES-GCM encrypts all widget cached data
- Widget key management: random 256-bit key in shared container
- PII audit: location coords and revenue data marked .private in logs
- Client-side throttling: WeatherKit rate limiter (30s min interval)
- JSON deserialization validation: crash-safe decode with error logging

UI Polish:
- LiquidGlassCard: cool/neutral Apple-style frosted glass (removed yellowish tones)
- ambientGradient: neutral cool tones for light/dark mode
- Widget glass background: accent-color overlay removed, neutral white borders
- ScoreRing: modern X/10 display with smooth animations
- HeroCard: refined layout with integrated temperature display

Localization:
- Em dashes replaced with hyphens across all files
- Key event notifications: numerical data removed, only event timing shown
- Rain risk messages: merged format with time range and percentage
- Ad localization strings: full EN + TR support